title: If You Believe You Deserve Luxury Look No Further.
posting_body: Our community is now offering in-person tours by appointment only.
Please ensure that tours are limited to two guests and masks must be worn throughout the tour.
Please contact our leasing office to schedule your tour today!
Please call or email us today.
We currently have a 2 bedroom 2 bath available.
within our small gated community that's secluded and surrounded by a lush greenbelt.
However, our most appealing feature is our location, we are minutes from Downtown Seattle and Renton, but nestled in a tranquil nature setting.
Taylor Creek truly creates a sophisticated interaction between modern conveniences and environmental simplicity.
We are open Monday through Friday from 9am to 6pm and CLOSED on Saturday's and Sunday's.
